# HTML Shell Rules

- `index.html` is the app shell, not a framework template.
- Preserve ids, template structure, and `data-action` hooks unless the task explicitly includes updating their consumers.
- Remember that the shell supports both the title/creation flow and in-run overlays.
- Any structural UI change should be checked against mobile usability.
